edu.harvard.hms.dbmi.bd2k.irct.model.ontology

Class Path

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.harvard.hms.dbmi.bd2k.irct.model.ontology.Path

  • public class Path
extends java.lang.Object
    The Path class represents a path in a resource. Paths can be linked to other paths through ontology relationships.
    Author:
    Jeremy R. Easton-Marks
